Societal Awareness

Categories of people (including marriage encouragement, social acceptance, recruitment of women into unions, workshops, discussions etc.) awareness would assist in minimising abortion risks. Awareness of the importance of leading a healthy sexual life would greatly help curb the risks alerting women of the dangers of abortions.

Police Powers

Parties that carry out these policies ought to be imprisoned. Political groups such as anti- abortion groups would dispatch

people to carry out their policies if the government favors their thinking for example in case of doctors.

The role of activists

To concur with sex education and family planning is what this category can to in order to improve in the state. The policy to tackle the death of women from unsafe abortions is the focus of Conscientious Objection (CO). In that case, removal of the abortion act is achieved by a wide range of protesters [Bansberg].

Conclusion

The use of fear and respect were also seen as a possible way of curbing abortions. Few states have tried restricting the abortion as a way of maintaining the determination of the peoplef to go for an abortion more substantially.
